#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the "Name" field of the "Staff" table</h2>
The name field contains the full name of the staff member in:
<div class=field_format>First Middle Last Suffixes</div>
order.  For instance:
<div class=field_format>Kermit Van Pelt Roosevelt Jr.</div>
When names are listed in searches, they will be listed this way, though they will be sorted by
last name.

